<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>🤖 智能助手 - GUCCANG</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/assistant.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 返回导航 -->
    <div class="nav-back">
        <a href="/main" class="back-btn">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i> 返回主页
        </a>
        <a href="/mcp" class="back-btn">
            <i class="fas fa-tools"></i> MCP管理
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <header class="assistant-header">
            <div class="assistant-title">
                <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                <h1>智能助手</h1>
                <span class="status-indicator online">在线</span>
            </div>
            <div class="assistant-subtitle">
                <p>您的个人数据分析师和生活教练</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- 导航标签 -->
        <nav class="assistant-nav">
            <div class="nav-tabs">
                <button class="nav-tab active" data-tab="assistant" onclick="switchTab('assistant')">
                    <i class="fas fa-robot"></i> 智能助手
                </button>
                <button class="nav-tab" data-tab="health" onclick="switchTab('health')">
                    <i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> 健康状态
                </button>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <main class="assistant-main">
            <!-- 智能助手内容 -->
            <div id="assistant-content" class="tab-content active">
                <!-- 左侧：聊天界面 -->
                <section class="chat-section">
                <div class="chat-container">
                    <div class="chat-messages" id="chatMessages">
                        <!-- 欢迎消息 -->
                        <div class="message assistant-message">
                            <div class="avatar">
                                <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="message-content">
                                <div class="message-text">
                                    <p>您好！我是您的智能助手，现在配备了强大的MCP工具支持！</p>
                                    <p>我可以帮您：</p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>📊 使用MCP工具分析您的个人数据和行为模式</li>
                                        <li>💡 基于工具调用提供个性化的建议和提醒</li>
                                        <li>📋 通过工具集成帮助管理任务和计划</li>
                                        <li>📈 调用外部工具生成各种统计报告</li>
                                        <li>🎯 使用专业工具追踪目标进度和成就</li>
                                        <li>🔧 <strong>新功能：智能工具调用</strong> - 根据需求自动选择合适的MCP工具</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>试试问我："使用MCP工具帮我分析最近的数据"或"调用工具帮我优化时间分配"</p>
                                    <p><em>提示：您可以在右侧工具面板中选择特定的MCP工具，或让我自动选择最合适的工具。</em></p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="message-time">刚刚</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="chat-input-container">
                        <div class="quick-actions">
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="status">📊 状态分析</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="time">⏰ 时间分析</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="goals">🎯 目标进度</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="suggestions">💡 智能建议</button>
                            <button class="quick-btn" data-action="tools" onclick="showMCPToolsDialog()">🔧 工具</button>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="input-wrapper">
                            <input type="text" id="messageInput" placeholder="问问我任何关于您的数据或计划的问题..." maxlength="500">
                            <button class="send-btn" id="sendBtn">
                                <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- 右侧：智能面板 -->
            <aside class="info-panel">
                <div class="panel-header">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> 数据概览</h3>
                    <button class="refresh-btn" id="refreshData">
                        <i class="fas fa-refresh"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>

                <!-- 今日概览 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-calendar-day"></i> 今日概览</h4>
                    <div class="stats-grid">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-value" id="todayTasks">-</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">任务完成</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-value" id="todayReading">-</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">阅读进度</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-value" id="todayExercise">-</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">锻炼记录</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <div class="stat-value" id="todayBlogs">-</div>
                            <div class="stat-label">博客写作</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 聊天历史 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-history"></i> 聊天历史</h4>
                    <div class="chat-history-controls">
                        <input type="date" id="chatHistoryDate" class="date-input" title="选择日期查看聊天历史">
                        <button class="load-history-btn" id="loadHistoryBtn" onclick="loadSelectedDateHistory()">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i> 加载
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="history-info">
                        <small>选择日期查看对应的聊天记录</small>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 智能建议 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> 智能建议</h4>
                    <div class="suggestions-list" id="suggestionsList">
                        <div class="suggestion-item">
                            <div class="suggestion-icon">💡</div>
                            <div class="suggestion-text">正在分析您的数据...</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 快速操作 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> 快速操作</h4>
                    <div class="quick-operations">
                        <button class="operation-btn" data-action="new-task">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> 新建任务
                        </button>
                        <button class="operation-btn" data-action="record-exercise">
                            <i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i> 记录锻炼
                        </button>
                        <button class="operation-btn" data-action="write-blog">
                            <i class="fas fa-pen"></i> 写博客
                        </button>
                        <button class="operation-btn" data-action="add-reading">
                            <i class="fas fa-book"></i> 添加阅读
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 趋势图表 -->
                <div class="info-card">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-area"></i> 近期趋势</h4>
                    <div class="chart-container">
                        <canvas id="trendChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>
            </div>

            <!-- 健康状态内容 -->
            <div id="health-content" class="tab-content">
                <div class="health-dashboard">
                    <!-- 综合健康状态概览 -->
                    <div class="health-overview">
                        <div class="comprehensive-health-card">
                            <div class="health-header">
                                <h3><i class="fas fa-heart"></i><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> 综合健康状态
                                    <button class="algorithm-info-btn" onclick="showAlgorithmInfo('overall')" title="查看算法说明">
                                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </h3>
                                <div class="overall-score">
                                    <span class="score-value" id="overallHealthScore">82</span>
                                    <span class="score-label">分</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- 6个健康维度评分 -->
                            <div class="health-dimensions">
                                <div class="dimension-item mental">
                                    <div class="dimension-icon">🧠</div>
                                    <div class="dimension-info">
                                        <div class="dimension-score" id="mentalScore">78</div>
                                        <div class="dimension-label">心理健康</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="dimension-item physical">
                                    <div class="dimension-icon">💪</div>
                                    <div class="dimension-info">
                                        <div class="dimension-score" id="physicalScore">92</div>
                                        <div class="dimension-label">体能健康</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="dimension-item learning">
                                    <div class="dimension-icon">📚</div>
                                    <div class="dimension-info">
                                        <div class="dimension-score" id="learningScore">88</div>
                                        <div class="dimension-label">学习成长</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="dimension-item time">
                                    <div class="dimension-icon">⏰</div>
                                    <div class="dimension-info">
                                        <div class="dimension-score" id="timeScore">75</div>
                                        <div class="dimension-label">时间管理</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="dimension-item goal">
                                    <div class="dimension-icon">🎯</div>
                                    <div class="dimension-info">
                                        <div class="dimension-score" id="goalScore">82</div>
                                        <div class="dimension-label">目标执行</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="dimension-item balance">
                                    <div class="dimension-icon">⚖️</div>
                                    <div class="dimension-info">
                                        <div class="dimension-score" id="balanceScore">85</div>
                                        <div class="dimension-label">生活平衡</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 心理健康专区 -->
                    <div class="mental-health-section">
                        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> 心理健康监测</h3>
                        <div class="mental-health-cards">
                            <!-- 压力监测 -->
                            <div class="mental-card stress-monitor">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> 压力水平
                                    <button class="algorithm-info-btn" onclick="showAlgorithmInfo('stress')" title="查看算法说明">
                                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </h4>
                                <div class="stress-level">
                                    <div class="stress-gauge">
                                        <div class="gauge-bg">
                                            <div class="gauge-fill" id="stressGauge" style="width: 45%"></div>
                                        </div>
                                        <span class="stress-value" id="stressValue">中等</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="stress-details">
                                        <div class="stress-factor">
                                            <span class="factor-label">未完成任务:</span>
                                            <span class="factor-value" id="unfinishedTasks">8项</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="stress-factor">
                                            <span class="factor-label">紧急任务:</span>
                                            <span class="factor-value" id="urgentTasks">2项</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="stress-recommendation">
                                            💡 建议: 优先处理紧急任务
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 情绪健康 -->
                            <div class="mental-card emotion-tracker">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-smile"></i> 情绪健康
                                    <button class="algorithm-info-btn" onclick="showAlgorithmInfo('emotion')" title="查看算法说明">
                                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </h4>
                                <div class="emotion-status">
                                    <div class="emotion-stability">
                                        <span class="stability-label">情绪稳定度:</span>
                                        <span class="stability-value" id="emotionStability">良好</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="emotion-trend">
                                        <span class="trend-label">最近7天情绪趋势:</span>
                                        <div class="emotion-icons" id="emotionTrend">
                                            <span>😊</span><span>😊</span><span>😐</span><span>😊</span>
                                            <span>😊</span><span>😔</span><span>😊</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="emotion-stats">
                                        <div class="emotion-stat">
                                            <span class="stat-label">积极表达:</span>
                                            <span class="stat-value" id="positiveExpression">78%</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="emotion-stat">
                                            <span class="stat-label">情绪丰富度:</span>
                                            <span class="stat-value" id="emotionRichness">高</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 焦虑风险评估 -->
                            <div class="mental-card anxiety-assessment">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> 焦虑风险
                                    <button class="algorithm-info-btn" onclick="showAlgorithmInfo('anxiety')" title="查看算法说明">
                                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </h4>
                                <div class="anxiety-risk">
                                    <div class="risk-level">
                                        <span class="risk-label">当前风险等级:</span>
                                        <span class="risk-value low-medium" id="anxietyRisk">低-中等</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="risk-factors">
                                        <div class="risk-factor">
                                            <span class="factor-name">作息规律:</span>
                                            <div class="rating-stars">
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star">☆</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="risk-factor">
                                            <span class="factor-name">任务管理:</span>
                                            <div class="rating-stars">
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star">☆</span>
                                                <span class="star">☆</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="risk-factor">
                                            <span class="factor-name">社交活跃:</span>
                                            <div class="rating-stars">
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                                <span class="star filled">⭐</span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="anxiety-detail">
                                        <span class="detail-text">深夜活动: <strong id="lateNightActivity">2次/周</strong></span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 心理健康建议 -->
                            <div class="mental-card mental-recommendations">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> 心理健康建议</h4>
                                <div class="mental-tips" id="mentalHealthTips">
                                    <div class="tip-item meditation">
                                        <div class="tip-icon">🧘</div>
                                        <div class="tip-text">建议增加冥想/放松时间</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="tip-item sleep">
                                        <div class="tip-icon">🌅</div>
                                        <div class="tip-text">尝试早起，减少深夜活动</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="tip-item social">
                                        <div class="tip-icon">👥</div>
                                        <div class="tip-text">本周社交互动较少，建议主动参与讨论</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="tip-item journal">
                                        <div class="tip-icon">📝</div>
                                        <div class="tip-text">写作情绪偏负面，建议记录积极事件</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 核心指标卡片区域 -->
                    <div class="core-metrics-section">
                        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> 核心健康指标</h3>
                        <div class="core-metrics-grid">
                            <!-- 今日运动状态 -->
                            <div class="metric-card fitness">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-running"></i> 今日运动状态
                                    <button class="algorithm-info-btn" onclick="showAlgorithmInfo('fitness')" title="查看算法说明">
                                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </h4>
                                <div class="metric-content">
                                    <div class="metric-main">
                                        <span class="metric-value" id="weeklyExercise">3</span>
                                        <span class="metric-unit">/3次</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="metric-label">本周已运动</div>
                                    <div class="metric-details">
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">今日消耗:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="todayCalories">320卡路里</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">主要锻炼:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="mainExercise">有氧运动 45分钟</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 学习进度跟踪 -->
                            <div class="metric-card learning">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-book"></i> 学习进度</h4>
                                <div class="metric-content">
                                    <div class="metric-main">
                                        <span class="metric-value" id="monthlyReadingProgress">65</span>
                                        <span class="metric-unit">%</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="metric-label">本月阅读进度</div>
                                    <div class="metric-details">
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">在读书籍:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="currentBook">《深度工作》</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">本周写作:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="weeklyWriting">3篇, 2400字</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 时间效能分析 -->
                            <div class="metric-card time-management">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 时间效能
                                    <button class="algorithm-info-btn" onclick="showAlgorithmInfo('timeManagement')" title="查看算法说明">
                                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                                    </button>
                                </h4>
                                <div class="metric-content">
                                    <div class="metric-main">
                                        <span class="metric-value" id="timeEfficiency">良好</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="metric-label">作息规律度</div>
                                    <div class="metric-details">
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">活跃时段:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="activeHours">9-11点, 14-17点</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">连续规律:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="routineStreak">7天</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 任务执行情况 -->
                            <div class="metric-card goal-execution">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> 任务执行</h4>
                                <div class="metric-content">
                                    <div class="metric-main">
                                        <span class="metric-value" id="dailyTaskCompletion">6</span>
                                        <span class="metric-unit">/8</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="metric-label">今日任务完成</div>
                                    <div class="metric-details">
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">本月目标:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="monthlyGoals">已达成 8/10 项</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">连续完成:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="completionStreak">5天</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 生活节奏评估 -->
                            <div class="metric-card life-balance">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i> 生活节奏</h4>
                                <div class="metric-content">
                                    <div class="metric-main">
                                        <span class="metric-value" id="workLifeBalance">平衡</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="metric-label">工作生活平衡</div>
                                    <div class="metric-details">
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">工作学习:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="workStudyHours">8小时 (合理)</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">社交互动:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="socialInteraction">本周5次</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 趋势预测 -->
                            <div class="metric-card trend-prediction">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> 趋势预测</h4>
                                <div class="metric-content">
                                    <div class="metric-main">
                                        <span class="metric-value trend-up" id="healthTrend">↗️ 稳步上升</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="metric-label">健康趋势</div>
                                    <div class="metric-details">
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">数据基础:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value">最近30天</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="detail-item">
                                            <span class="detail-label">预计月底:</span>
                                            <span class="detail-value" id="predictedScore">87分</span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 数据可视化区域 -->
                    <div class="health-visualization-section">
                        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i> 健康数据可视化</h3>
                        <div class="visualization-grid">
                            <!-- 健康雷达图 -->
                            <div class="chart-card radar-chart">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-radar"></i> 健康维度雷达图</h4>
                                <div class="chart-container">
                                    <canvas id="healthRadarChart"></canvas>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 情绪波动曲线 -->
                            <div class="chart-card emotion-chart">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> 情绪波动趋势</h4>
                                <div class="chart-container">
                                    <canvas id="emotionTrendChart"></canvas>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 压力热力图 -->
                            <div class="chart-card stress-heatmap">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-fire"></i> 压力水平热力图</h4>
                                <div class="chart-container">
                                    <canvas id="stressHeatmapChart"></canvas>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 时间分布图 -->
                            <div class="chart-card time-distribution">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 时间分布分析</h4>
                                <div class="chart-container">
                                    <canvas id="timeDistributionChart"></canvas>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 社交健康指标 -->
                            <div class="chart-card social-health">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-users"></i> 社交健康指标</h4>
                                <div class="chart-container">
                                    <canvas id="socialHealthChart"></canvas>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- 心理韧性趋势 -->
                            <div class="chart-card resilience-trend">
                                <h4><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> 心理韧性趋势</h4>
                                <div class="chart-container">
                                    <canvas id="resilienceTrendChart"></canvas>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <!-- MCP工具管理大面板 -->
        <section class="mcp-tools-panel">
            <div class="mcp-tools-panel-header">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-tools"></i> MCP 工具管理中心</h3>
                <div class="mcp-tools-panel-actions">
                    <button class="mcp-panel-toggle" onclick="toggleMCPPanel()">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-up"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mcp-tools-panel-content" id="mcp-tools-panel-content">
                <div id="mcp-tools-status-large" class="mcp-tools-status-large">
                    <div class="mcp-status-loading">
                        <i class="fas fa-spinner fa-spin"></i>
                        <span>正在加载MCP工具...</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mcp-info-large">
                    <div class="mcp-info-grid">
                        <div class="mcp-info-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>工具选择</strong>
                                <p>选择要在对话中使用的MCP工具。未选择时将使用所有可用工具。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mcp-info-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-server"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>服务器状态</strong>
                                <p>实时显示各个MCP服务器的连接状态和可用工具数量。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mcp-info-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>搜索功能</strong>
                                <p>支持按工具名称、服务器或描述进行快速搜索和过滤。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mcp-info-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>配置管理</strong>
                                <p>可前往<a href="/mcp">MCP配置页面</a>管理服务器和工具配置。</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 设置面板 -->
        <div class="settings-panel" id="settingsPanel">
            <div class="settings-header">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> 助手设置</h3>
                <button class="close-btn" id="closeSettings">
                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="settings-content">
                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h4>通知设置</h4>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label class="switch">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="enableNotifications" checked>
                            <span class="slider"></span>
                        </label>
                        <span>启用智能提醒</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label class="switch">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="enableSuggestions" checked>
                            <span class="slider"></span>
                        </label>
                        <span>显示智能建议</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h4>分析深度</h4>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label>分析时间范围:</label>
                        <select id="analysisRange">
                            <option value="7">最近7天</option>
                            <option value="30" selected>最近30天</option>
                            <option value="90">最近90天</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h4>个性化</h4>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label>助手人格:</label>
                        <select id="assistantPersonality">
                            <option value="friendly">友好温和</option>
                            <option value="professional" selected>专业严谨</option>
                            <option value="encouraging">鼓励激励</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="setting-group">
                    <h4>显示效果</h4>
                    <div class="setting-item">
                        <label class="switch">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="enableTypingEffect" checked>
                            <span class="slider"></span>
                        </label>
                        <span>启用打字机光标效果</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="setting-description">
                        <small>注：响应内容将实时流式显示，此选项仅控制打字机光标的显示</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 设置按钮 -->
        <button class="settings-btn" id="settingsBtn">
            <i class="fas fa-cog"></i>
        </button>

        <!-- 算法说明弹窗 -->
        <div class="algorithm-info-modal" id="algorithmInfoModal">
            <div class="algorithm-info-content">
                <div class="algorithm-info-header">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> 算法说明</h3>
                    <button class="close-btn" onclick="closeAlgorithmInfo()">
                        <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="algorithm-info-body" id="algorithmInfoBody">
                    <!-- 算法详情内容将在这里动态插入 -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/marked/marked.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/assistant.js"></script>
</body>
</html>